                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border-t border-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 mt-8 pt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
                    &copy; 2025 Dynamic Blog. All rights reserved. 
                    <span class="mx-2">|</span>
                    <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">Privacy Policy</a>
                    <span class="mx-2">|</span>
